, 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1096-3642.1986.tb01810.x" author="Rudman, WB" journalOrPublisher="Zoological Journal Linnean Society" pageId="22" pageNumber="31" pagination="101 - 184" refId="B20" refString="Rudman, WB, 1986a. The Chromodorididae (Opisthobranchia, Mollusca) of the Indo-West Pacific: the genus Glossodoris Ehrenberg (= Casella Hancock and A. Adams). Zoological Journal Linnean Society 86 (2): 101 - 184, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1096-3642.1986.tb01810.x" title="The Chromodorididae (Opisthobranchia, Mollusca) of the Indo-West Pacific: the genus Glossodoris Ehrenberg (= Casella Hancock and A. Adams)." url="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1096-3642.1986.tb01810.x" volume="86" year="1986 a">1986a</bibRefCitation>
